name: IndexedCollection_uniqueIndexedCollectionTest
description: Unit tests for the uniqueIndexedCollection method of the IndexedCollection class.

test_cases.name: testUniqueIndexedCollectionWithUniqueKeys
test_cases.description: Tests the uniqueIndexedCollection method with a collection of unique keys.

test_cases.name: testUniqueIndexedCollectionWithDuplicateKeys
test_cases.description: Tests the uniqueIndexedCollection method with a collection containing duplicate keys, expecting an IllegalArgumentException.

test_cases.name: testUniqueIndexedCollectionWithEmptyCollection
test_cases.description: Tests the uniqueIndexedCollection method with an empty collection.

test_cases.name: testUniqueIndexedCollectionWithNullKeyTransformer
test_cases.description: Tests the uniqueIndexedCollection method with a null key transformer, expecting a NullPointerException.
